{"tid":1589971,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"怕咗魔迷！普巴買洛威拿看門口","createTime":"2019-09-23T13:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T17:06:18.000Z","uid":322766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"afbd5c4adf4c2e9a2ef1ddfc29ba77580416feb8","tid":1589971,"uid":322766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】為了避免球迷騷擾，曼聯中場普巴花重金購買惡犬洛威拿保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n普巴（Paul Pogba）今夏公開要求轉會不成，被逼留在曼聯，但表現仍然平庸，最近更因傷缺陣多場。不少紅魔球迷對這名26歲法國國腳非常不滿，更在球會訓練場外噴上「Pogba Out（普巴走人）」字樣。<br />\n<br />\n由於害怕被憤怒的魔迷騷擾，普巴最近從狗隻專家公司Chaperone K9，以15000萬鎊購入一隻洛威拿，以作看門口之用。普巴隊友華舒福、菲爾鍾斯早前亦有幫趁Chaperone K9。<br />\n<br />\nChaperone K9老闆李察阿奴說：「足球員很容易成為別人的目標，他們希望保護家人安全。除非主人給予指令，這些狗隻並不危險。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f119e4e23cc8961037702260ee81af484f14de3e","tid":1589971,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"553ba1a95633b1c26002ef6e59ff6d366cd58560","tid":1589971,"uid":322766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f119e4e23cc8961037702260ee81af484f14de3e","tid":1589971,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"快到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\